These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: soy-milk, tea, fanta, juice
Pet: bird, hedgehog, ferret, frog
1. Pet:frog is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1
2. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Pet:hedgehog##1
3. Beverage:juice is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:frog##3
5. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea | juice | fanta |
| Pet        | bird | hedgehog   | frog | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, zombie, mystery, action
Nationality: malaysian, canadian, british, pakistani
1. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1
2. Nationality:malaysian is on the left of Nationality:british##1
3. Nationality:british is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Nationality:canadian is on the right of Nationality:british##1
6. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | adventure  | zombie  | action |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | malaysian | british | canadian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: pear, broccoli, nectarine, papaya
Movie-Genre: time-travel, adventure, drama, thriller
1. Food:papaya is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:thriller##3
2. Food:nectarine is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the left or right of Food:broccoli##3
4. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the right of Movie-Genre:drama##1
5. Movie-Genre:time-travel is in an odd position##4
6. Food:broccoli is on the right of Food:nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | papaya | nectarine | broccoli    | pear      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | thriller     | time-travel | adventure |

