.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: card-games, board-games, singing, filmmaking
Music-Genre: soul, salsa, ambient, jazz
1. Hobby:board-games is between Music-Genre:soul and Music-Genre:jazz##2
2. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
3. Music-Genre:ambient is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | card-games | board-games | singing |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | soul   | salsa    | jazz  |

