.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: d&b, rock, soul, ambient
Nationality: japanese, egyptian, mexican, chinese
1. Music-Genre:soul is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Nationality:egyptian == Music-Genre:ambient##1
3. Nationality:mexican is on the right of Music-Genre:d&b##1
4. Music-Genre:rock is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:japanese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | d&b    | soul   | ambient       |
| Nationality   | japanese | chinese | mexican | egyptian |

