3. Beverage:coffee is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:peach is on the left of Food:apple##1
5. Food:apple is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
6. Food:peach is in an even position##4
7. Food:artichoke == Beverage:mirinda##1

